reviewText: Excelente  video. Lo recomendara  con cualquier persona. No me  cansare de verlo.  Muy buena resolucin para este  tipo de formato
Good price for the dvd. Haven't seen it yet, it was a gift for my mom since she grew up with Mafalda, but she loves it. She didn't even know there was a cartoon of Mafalda.
Este DVD es un clsico, hablado en espaol, Mafalda sigue siendo un referente en la poltica latinoamericana, vale la pena tenerlo.

A wonderful movie I was waiting to watch for years! Eventhough Quino is from Argentina and that's just at the other side of the mountains I was never able to find good deals for books, or the video it self here. Just lovely!
